{"tid":1631440,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"是時候說再見護膚化妝品 (empties, hit pan, declutter)","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T06:08:03.000Z","uid":57439,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9f09d58b7d0b97286b6110532329caf82cb6dd","tid":1631440,"uid":57439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"有時用完/hit pan 勁有成功感, 立此存照, 順手share 用後感<br />\n<br />\n夏天混油, 冬天混乾, 長期缺水, 常長粉刺中老肌<br />\n<br />\n平貴都用, 主要敵人: 懶<br />\n<br />\n1. Three 蜜粉 (empty)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yXvuck.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yXvuck.png&h=161a50d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中規中矩<br />\n夏天未算太控油, 但冬天又唔會乾<br />\n講唔上頂級細緻但finishing 又唔差<br />\n估計可以應付大部分皮膚,對得住價錢<br />\n<br />\n購自日本, 香港代理定價好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e17109560c6514998ae55f7adddc4c6f7ee2318","tid":1631440,"uid":57439,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"2. Tom ford 胭脂02 frantic pink<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/codFRCA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcodFRCA.png&h=5b7c3640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁有成功感既hit pan, 8g 都用到見底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最初買入覺得顏色無趣, 點知越用越順手, 配搭大部分妝都ok<br />\n<br />\n粉細顯色持久, 全部做到<br />\n<br />\n缺點就係比較貴, 貴買平用都合理<br />\n<br />\n希望用晒佢先停"},{"pid":"8bed876d275d4c7921f3ab3aaab589cb56b5cf4e","tid":1631440,"uid":220922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:14:20.000Z","msg":"返屋企又影下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137d305a757d8e8d6d1744f4bd837c73b29f0850","tid":1631440,"uid":220922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"Lunasol beige beige 百搭冇出錯既色<br />\n［img]<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/YGovgti.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"h